---
title: Parmesan Chicken Salad with Zesty Pesto Dressing
description: This satisfying salad is inspired by the classic Italian-American dish, Chicken Parmesan. Slow-cooked sauce is swapped out for sweet and juicy cherry tomatoes and a zesty pesto dressing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-poulet-style-parmigiana-afc2b138.jpg
